{"created_at": "Wed May 25 18:21:45 +0000 2022", "timestamp": "2022-05-25T18:21:45+00:00", "id": 1529528159930040320, "id_str": "1529528159930040320", "full_text": "So many transformer explanations want me to intuitively understand what's happening.  I just want to understand what the code does.  This is 25 lines of pure functional code which helped me, and might others.\n\nhttps://t.co/0LstU86SpO", "urls": ["https://github.com/awf/functional-transformer"], "images": [], "user_id": 53514472, "username": "Awfidius", "link": "https://twitter.com/Awfidius/status/1529528159930040320"}
